# Secret environment for the basic-delivery example.
#
# Copy to `secrets/.env` (gitignored) only when Smith or another configured
# coding agent needs environment variables. Temper does not read provider auth
# files or provider secrets; smith-worker simply inherits the environment for the
# configured agent command.
#
# Example: if ANVIL_AGENT_ARGS in config/temper.env selects a provider
# mode that reads a provider variable, set the secret here before starting the
# launcher.
#
# SMITH_PROVIDER_SECRET=...
# TEMPER_DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=...
#
# Forgejo admin tokens are minted by the launcher for the provision step and are
# not pasted here.
#
# TEMPER_FORGEJO_ADMIN_TOKEN=
